    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Process standards help to universalise best practice in organisational management, governance and internal control as a way to achieve good outcomes via organisation processes. Technical process standards institutionalise trust building practices such as risk and quality management. Some process standards are \u2018certifiable\u2019, meaning that organisations can be independently assessed as meeting \u2018good practice\u2019 and can receive a certification against that technical standard. For example, ISO/IEC CD 42001 - Information Technology - Artificial Intelligence - Management System."), mdx("li", {
